{"type": "article", "id": 13498, "title": "节水淋浴喷头", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-14T07:46:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135743bGS5oDd7A0pnJK2h.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t旧金山的 Nebia 公司最近推出了一款节水淋浴喷头，力求节约用水，合理利用水资源。它看起来很像一个圆圆的方向盘，其节水原理是采用多种喷嘴技术来改变水滴的分布和大小，从而扩大淋浴的面积，达到普通淋浴头的 10 倍，从而节省出 70% 的水量。除此之外，喷头外观看起来时尚简洁，简单的支架设计让它安装起来也非常简单。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1499369835/nebia-shower-better-experience-70-less-water\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141242OFpv6Jygi1ULhRef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79852941\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141243YndiJvLAHs0oKtbX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141243kyFPNlxzs0rbBEWV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54852941\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141243YmK6eWvaDPSTAjtM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.35\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141244Boyru012i4Tv5GeE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141244xtIWMyurmbqLUE8v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141244htCDf7zqEGZOBUoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n\n"}